Description:
Embrace a playful and artistic touch with our side table's cylindrical silhouette, featuring fluted edges reminiscent of ancient ruins' majestic pillars. This versatile piece is perfect for both outdoor lounge areas and indoor spaces, serving as a functional and stylish accent table. Crafted from lightweight concrete with an antique black finish, it offers a smooth and visually captivating surface. The subtle texture adds depth to any room, seamlessly blending into various decor styles. Please note that this product showcases the inherent beauty of natural materials, with variations in color, texture, grain, and minor imperfections like blemishes, scratches, marks, and cracks that only add to its natural charm.

Finish: Antique Black Finish with Acrylic Seal
Sealed and Treated for Indoor/Outdoor Use
